"'''Lucky'''" is a story from [[Star Wars Tales 23|''Star Wars Tales'' 23]] (later collected in ''[[Star Wars Tales Volume 6]]'' and ''[[Star Wars Legends Epic Collection: The New Republic Vol. 2]]'') that reveals more of the past of [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]]. The main part of the story is set in [[2 BBY/Legends|2 BBY]] while the framing story is several weeks after the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]].

==Plot summary==
The story centers on Wedge, showing how "lucky" he is, while he never gets what he really wants. The bulk of the story is a flashback, showing how Wedge first came to join the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebellion]].

On [[Gus Talon/Legends|Gus Talon]], Wedge has fallen in love with a girl named [[Mala Tinero|Mala]]. But Mala's father, [[Rallo]], is part of the Rebellion and, while Antilles is away, the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperials]] [[Bombing of Gus Talon|wipe out]] Gus Talon.

In the present, Wedge states that the he doesn't feel as lucky as others say he is, citing the incident at Gus Talon and his inability to stop it as an example.

==Continuity==
It was referenced in the [[Star Wars (2013) 10|tenth issue]] of the [[Star Wars (2013)|2013 ''Star Wars'' comic series]] (''[[Star Wars Volume 2: From the Ruins of Alderaan]]'') by Wedge Antilles himself.

The title page for ''Star Wars Tales'' 23 states that the events of "Lucky" take place "approximately seven [[Standard year/Legends|years]] before [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''Star Wars'': Episode IV ''A New Hope'']],"<ref name="Tales 23">[[Star Wars Tales 23|''Star Wars Tales'' 23]]</ref> which would correspond to the year [[7 BBY/Legends|7 BBY]].<ref name="NEC">''[[The New Essential Chronology]]''</ref> This runs contrary to the story itself, which states that its flashback events on Gus Talon take place six years before the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]],<ref name="Lucky">{{Tales|23|Lucky (comic story)}}</ref> which would correspond to the year [[2 BBY/Legends|2 BBY]].<ref name="Date">"[[Lucky (comic story)|Lucky]]" is set "a couple of [[Standard week/Legends|weeks]]" after the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]], which ''[[The New Essential Chronology]]'' dates to [[4 ABY/Legends|4 ABY]], while the story's flashback to the events on [[Gus Talon/Legends|Gus Talon]] take place "six [[Standard year/Legends|years]] earlier." ''[[The Essential Atlas]]'' further dates the Battle of Endor to [[Great ReSynchronization|39:3]], which is the first [[Standard month/Legends|month]] of the 4 [[Galactic Standard Calendar|ABY]] year (as exampled [[:Template:YearMathGRS|here]]), thus firmly placing the events of "Lucky" in 4 ABY as well and its flashback in [[2 BBY/Legends|2 BBY]].</ref> Given that the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] is in existence during the flashback events of "Lucky,"<ref name="Lucky" /> the 7 [[Galactic Standard Calendar|BBY]] date would also contradict the timeline for the Rebel Alliance's establishment in 2 BBY.<ref name="Warfare">''[[The Essential Guide to Warfare]]''</ref>

